<emphasis box="[501,744,1807,1829]" italics="true" pageId="180" pageNumber="181">Austroponera castanea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
: lateral and dorsal view of body and full-face view of head (CASENT0172341, April Nobile and www.antweb.org); world distribution of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Schmidt &amp; Shattuck" authorityYear="2014" box="[947,1085,1838,1860]" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Austroponera" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="180" pageNumber="181" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[947,1085,1838,1860]" italics="true" pageId="180" pageNumber="181">Austroponera</emphasis>
